text: Juan Manuel Celaya Hernández (born 1 September 1998) is a Mexican diver. He participated at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships, winning a medal. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male divers Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in diving Category:Pan American Games medalists in diving Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Mexico Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Mexico Category:Divers at the 2019 Pan American Games
